reviewText: In the Part 2's, they hide stuff. If this is out of stock, I hope someone who has this can upload this to Youtube and/or tell us what's hidden in Part 2.

My two year old loves this video.  It is filled with all types of tractors and takes you in the cab to see how they drive them.  The tractor pulls where also great to watch!  And best of all it came with tractor trading  cards which can be a great learning tool to go with the video!  If your  child loves tractors this is a great video to buy!
